snippet.title: City vs Verna vs Ciaz vs Vento vs Rapid vs Yaris - The Best Sedan Is... | Comparison | Autocar India
snippet.description:
The mid-size sedan segment has seen a lot of action in 2020 with new launches, facelifts and engine upgrades. But which is the pick of the segment? We've got the whole bunch together to find out. With us today are the fifth-gen Honda City, Hyundai Verna facelift, Volkswagen Vento TSI, Skoda Rapid TSI, Toyota Yaris and Maruti Suzuki Ciaz, and all of the cars are featured in their petrol-manual form. Renuka Kirpalani will be joined by Hormazd Sorabjee, Shapur Kotwal, Sergius Barretto, Gavin d'Souza Nikhil Bhatia and Saumil Shah in this mega comparison.

snippet.title: 2020 Honda City Review - Evolution or Revolution? | First Drive | Autocar India
snippet.description:
The City is Honda's most important model in India and it will soon be launched in an all-new avatar. Interestingly, however, this is the first time the old City will continue to be sold alongisde the new one. As a result the new model has grown up significantly and as Gavin D'Souza and Sergius Barretto find out, there's a lot to be excited for with the new model.
